What to do in Amsterdam?
Here you go!

Get the city in your smartphone, and enjoy your stay like a local.
City guide with all points of interest, and special venues selected by locals.

Purchase digital tickets via your smartphone; no printing required, skip the lines, use the speed lanes, and get discounts.

Detailed digital city map showing where you are and where your chosen venue is, including distance and navigation. Clearly marked shopping and nightlife areas.
With landmarks appearing as 3D drawings, very detailed city-center map, and overview map including suburbs and Schiphol airport.

Check the hotel page to stay in touch with your hotel, get information about the hotel and hotel services, and view the gallery. Options to book a room for your next stay.
Share your stay with your friends on social media.

This app is made by local specialists and contains detailed information about:
Restaurants, diamond museums, jewelers;
Attractions, museums, historical buildings;
Shopping areas, fashion stores, markets and squares;
Nightlife areas, clubs, pubs, coffeeshops (the Dutch kind);
Concert halls, theatres, guided tours;
Tram-, and taxi information, bike rental;
Nearby metro- and train stations.

Get Holland Brochure Services: City Guide now to find the things you NEED to do in Amsterdam and get your tickets ahead of time.
